{"tid":659772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(泡狗改不了吃屎) 韓亞航空接受大陸要求　將台灣列入「中國」","createTime":"2018-05-10T06:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T06:08:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f598c0200e1efb5d0fa131daa72244cf257726a9","tid":659772,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"中國大陸的反分裂行動席捲全球，多間外國航空公司近日都接到大陸民航局要求，標明台灣屬中國地區。韓媒報道，包括南韓航空業巨頭韓亞航空在內的多間公司，近日已應陸方要求，在官網上作出有關更改，另有部分公司則仍在討論標註地區的方式。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，韓亞航空官網的預訂頁面中，台灣已從「東南亞」一欄中，移到「中國大陸及港澳台」底下。部分航空公司處理與台灣相關訊息時，亦作出類似的變更。報導又援引南韓駐華使館人士稱，自1992年中韓建交開始，南韓就已經決定尊重「一個中國」的原則。<br />\n<br />\n就有關問題，大陸外交部發言人耿爽周日（6日）曾在記者會上表示，甚麼都改變不了世界上只有一個中國、港澳台地區是中國領土不可分割的一部分的客觀事實。他強調在大陸做生意的外國企業，應當尊重中國的主權和領土完整、尊重中國人民的民族感情。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180508/bkncn-20180508183809078-0508_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180508%2Fbkncn-20180508183809078-0508_05011_001.html&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FEU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=131c9bdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180508/bkncn-20180508183809078-0508_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf0e01f738beeb98113ecd3a6d9cbc007d103dd","tid":659772,"uid":186108,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲啲泡狗都列入埋我偉大的祖國"},{"pid":"45842071bf94d2db9646db3b4cc9a1aefa76785c","tid":659772,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"方便遲d一次過叫晒韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368161897eedda0c27037a633435c2adccbeeed1","tid":659772,"uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"「中國大陸及港澳台<span style=\"color: red;\">韓</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ccdbef7e642090d67f7bd391b7c4210ac7a61b","tid":659772,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20a6930b081e1438acc429da7b3cdc7b664bdf3","tid":659772,"uid":61529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:42:50.000Z","msg":"班台狗繼續崇韓啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d454b8b50cdfde06501fe603789e6868ebaf9b6f","tid":659772,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"中国= 支那鬼國<br />\n南朝鮮=南泡支那／朝鮮支那<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個民族一樣咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45b8edebed1f7783a0b67cd4154329258042568","tid":659772,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45842071bf94d2db9646db3b4cc9a1aefa76785c","tid":659772,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"方便遲d一次過叫晒韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"一齊叫朝鮮"},{"pid":"895ce2da79bed0ba55856162aed36e0fe1893116","tid":659772,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"德國畀左膠佔領咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而英國有史以來都係國際契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d21810bfef1c14b903dc53f7532ee9e60795c48","tid":659772,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"acf0e01f738beeb98113ecd3a6d9cbc007d103dd","tid":659772,"uid":186108,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲啲泡狗都列入埋我偉大的祖國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33